            <title><![CDATA[【[衰]原来忌辛辣不能吃葱姜蒜！】服用抗生素、滋阴清热、治疗湿热偏重和调理脾胃的药物期间都要忌辛辣[允悲]辛辣食物不仅会抵消药物的疗效，还可能增加原发疾病...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>原来忌辛辣不能吃葱姜蒜！】服用抗生素、滋阴清热、治疗湿热偏重和调理脾胃的药物期间都要忌辛辣<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>辛辣食物不仅会抵消药物的疗效，还可能增加原发疾病发作风险。除了辣椒外，大蒜、洋葱、大葱、芥末、生姜以及酒类，都属于辛辣食物。 <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[傻眼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shayan-4e8000eba9.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6Wj5t6l" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
